data.description: Come see this beautiful 3BR/2BA ranch in Winston. Updated kitchen and baths featuring custom cabinets and stainless steel appliances. Watch the sunset from your covered side porch off the kitchen. Home is on a corner lot a little over a half acre. Also there is a new electrical panel, some new wiring, an outside storage building. All flooring is vinyl plank tile except Master Bedroom.Ring doorbell not staying.
